<section class="intro-section">
    <p>Heart disease research is evolving rapidly, with experts challenging long-held assumptions and exploring new paradigms. This page presents diverse perspectives from cardiologists, researchers, and thought leaders - some mainstream, some contrarian, all contributing to our understanding of cardiovascular health.</p>

    <div class="key-point">
        <h3>Why Diverse Perspectives Matter</h3>
        <p>Science advances through debate and the testing of competing hypotheses. We present experts with varying viewpoints not to create confusion, but to demonstrate that cardiovascular medicine is a dynamic field where new evidence continually reshapes understanding. Readers should evaluate evidence critically and consult their own healthcare providers.</p>
    </div>
</section>

