            <blockquote>
                "ApoB is the best predictor of cardiovascular risk we have. But context matters enormously. A high apoB in someone with metabolic dysfunction is very different from someone who is metabolically healthy. We need to think about lipids as part of a system, not as isolated numbers."
            </blockquote>
