<section class="conclusion">
    <h2>Making Sense of Diverse Perspectives</h2>

    <p>The experts on this page represent a range of viewpoints - some mainstream, some alternative, some in between. This diversity reflects the genuine complexity of cardiovascular science and the ongoing evolution of our understanding.</p>

    <div class="key-point">
